SUMMARY:Maundy Thursday Service
DESCRIPTION:Join us on April 2nd at 7 PM in the Sanctuary for our Maundy Thursday service. We will gather for a time of reflection and Holy Communion as we remember the night Jesus shared with his disciples. \n“A new command I give you: Love one another. As I have loved you\, so you must love one another.” – John 13:34 \nAll are truly welcome to participate in the bread and cup or simply observe the service in peace. We look forward to seeing you there.
URL:https://apostlesucc.org/event/maundy-thursday-service/
LOCATION:Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://apostlesucc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Maundy-Thursday-2026-FB.jpg
END:VEVENT
