SUMMARY:Finance Committee Meeting
DESCRIPTION:When: Second Thursday of the Month at 12:30 PM \nWhere: Compassion Corner (Rm 107) \nThe Finance Committee supports the congregation by promoting responsible stewardship and providing oversight of the church’s finances. The committee plans and executes year-round stewardship efforts\, including annual campaigns for pledges of time\, talent\, and financial contributions. Additionally\, the committee promotes planned giving opportunities\, such as gifts from estates\, wills\, trusts\, annuities\, insurance policies\, and outright donations of money\, securities\, or property.
URL:https://apostlesucc.org/event/finance-committee-meeting-13/
LOCATION:Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
END:VEVENT
