SUMMARY:Annual Garage Sale Day 1
DESCRIPTION:Searching for a massive\, budget-friendly yard sale in or near Lancaster? Look no further!\nJoin us at Church of the Apostles UCC for our annual garage sale held on the Friday and Saturday following Easter. Be prepared to shop early\, as there’s always a long line before doors open on Friday! \nThis years sale is set for April 10th from 8 AM – 2 PM & April 11th from 8 AM – 1 PM in and around Fellowship Hall. Our address is 1850 Marietta Avenue\, Lancaster PA. Be sure to follow signs for Fellowship Hall! \nAll are welcome to attend this fun-filled annual event. We have many low-priced items for you to browse through including clothing\, collectables\, home furnishings\, jewelry\, sports items\, tools\, toys and so much more! Food options include hotdogs\, sodas and baked goods on Friday and Saturday! Ample parking\, including accessible parking\, is available on both days. \nIf you are interested in donating items\, you can do so the week of the sale\, April 6th\, 7th\, & 8th\, from 9 AM – 9 PM\, or April 9th\, from 9 AM – 12 PM\, by the Fellowship Hall doors. For additional information\, please feel free to contact us at office@apostlesucc.org or by calling (717) 392-5718. \nDownload a Poster to Share!\nList of donatable items!
URL:https://apostlesucc.org/event/annual-garage-sale-day-1/
LOCATION:Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://apostlesucc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Garage-Sale-2026-Flyer.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
