SUMMARY:Apostles Academy Concerts: Kutztown University Choirs
DESCRIPTION:oin us for an inspiring afternoon of music as the Kutztown University Choirs present a diverse and engaging choral concert on Sunday\, April 12\, 2026 at 3 PM in the Sanctuary at Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA. \nEnjoy the talent and artistry of these exceptional student vocalists as they share a wide-ranging program sure to uplift and move you. \n🎟 Free to attend! A free-will offering will be collected in lieu of tickets.♿ Our building is fully accessible with ample handicap parking available. \nAll are welcome\, bring a friend and experience the joy of live choral music!
