SUMMARY:Apostles Academy Presents: Bill Hager\, Storyteller & Photographer
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special evening with Lancaster photographer and storyteller Bill Hager as he presents “Brannigan’s Hollow and The Wood Spirit” on Saturday\, April 18\, 2026 at 7 PM at Church of the Apostles UCC\, 1850 Marietta Ave\, Lancaster\, PA. \nThrough captivating images and heartfelt storytelling\, Bill brings to life the magic\, mystery\, and meaning found in his original works. \n🎟 Free to attend! A free-will offering will be collected in lieu of tickets.♿ Our building is fully accessible with plenty of handicap parking available. \nDon’t miss this one-of-a-kind experience\, bring a friend and be inspired by the art of story and image.
URL:https://apostlesucc.org/event/apostles-academy-presents-bill-hager-storyteller-photographer/
